## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="db565-105">Poniższy C# przykład pokazuje, jak pobrać pierwszych 30 wpisów w zestawie wyników.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="db565-105">The following C# example shows how to retrieve the first 30 entries in a result set.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
using System.DirectoryServices;  
...  
DirectorySearcher src = new DirectorySearcher("…");   
src.VirtualListView = new DirectoryVirtualListView(0,30);  
foreach(SearchResult res in src.FindAll() )  
{  
    Console.WriteLine(…");  
}  
  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="db565-106">Poniższy C# przykład pokazuje, jak pobrać pierwsze 50 wpisów w zestawie wyników, który rozpoczyna się od liter "ha".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="db565-106">The following C# example shows how to retrieve the first 50 entries in a result set that start with the letters "Ha".</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
using System.DirectoryServices;  
...  
DirectorySearcher src = new DirectorySearcher("…");   
src.VirtualListView = new DirectoryVirtualListView(0,50, "Ha");  
foreach(SearchResult res in src.FindAll() )  
{  
    Console.WriteLine(…");  
}  
  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="db565-107">Poniższy C# przykład pokazuje, jak pobrać pierwsze 100 wpisów na 60% przybliżony cel.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="db565-107">The following C# example shows how to retrieve the first 100 entries at the 60% approximate target.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
using System.DirectoryServices;  
...  
// First VLV calls.   
DirectorySearcher src = new DirectorySearcher("…");   
src.VirtualListView = new DirectoryVirtualListView(100);  
foreach(SearchResult res in src.FindAll() )  
{  
    Console.WriteLine(…");  
}  
  
// Second Call, the VLV context is still attached to the DirectorySearcher.  
src.VirtualListView.TargetPercentage = 60;  
src.VirtualListView.BeforeCount = 50;  
src.VirtualListView.AfterCount = 50;  
  
foreach(SearchResult res in src.FindAll() )  
{  
    Console.WriteLine(…");  
}  
  
```
